Use this README file to introduce your application and point to useful places in the API for learning more.

This file is located in the following location:

doc/README_FOR_APP




=== COMMENTING SOURCE CODE



1) Please review the Documenting Source Code section at the following link from RDOC for the correct syntax of code comments

http://rdoc.rubyforge.org/RDoc/Markup.html





=== GENERATING/UPDATING THE RDOC README



1) To update your machine with the correct RDOC settings run:

rake lib/tasks/documentation.rake



2) To generate API documentation for your models, controllers, helpers, and libraries run:

rake doc:app